The paper discusses a security vulnerability in keyboard password entry, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The study also involves collecting data from users, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of thermal imaging technology to recover passwords falls under the category of cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) and signal processing (cs.SI). Finally, the paper proposes mitigation strategies, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE).
